In this article, President Trump emphasizes the importance of financial literacy in unlocking the American Dream. He discusses how his administration is working to enhance the financial education and capability of all Americans through the Financial Literacy and Education Commission. Various government departments, such as the Department of Housing and Urban Development and the Department of Education, are implementing initiatives to educate Americans on financial management, homeownership, and student loans. The article also highlights the efforts to encourage partnerships between government, the private sector, and higher education institutions to support financial education and skills training. President Trump encourages all Americans to become more financially knowledgeable to fully participate in the dynamic economy and ensure prosperity for themselves, their families, and future generations.